---
// Last Light — GitHub maintenance agent
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8" />
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
	<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/logo.png" />
	<title>Last Light — GitHub Maintenance Agent</title>
	<meta name="description" content="An open-source agent that keeps the lights on in your GitHub repos. Triages issues, reviews PRs, monitors repo health — so you can focus elsewhere." />
	<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
	<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
	<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;600&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>

	<!-- Hero -->
	<header class="hero">
		<div class="hero-content">
			<img src="/logo.png" alt="Last Light logo" class="hero-logo" />
			<p class="hero-name">Last Light</p>
			<h1>Keep the lights on <span class="accent">after you've moved on</span></h1>
			<p class="subtitle">
				An open-source agent that looks after repos in maintenance mode.
				Triages issues, reviews PRs, chases down stale items — so you can focus on what's next.
			</p>
			<div class="hero-actions">
				<a href="#get-started" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
				<a href="https://github.com/cliftonc/lastlight" class="btn btn-ghost" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View Source</a>
				<a href="https://github.com/users/cliftonc/projects/4" class="btn btn-ghost" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Roadmap</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</header>

	<!-- What it does -->
	<section class="features" id="features">
		<h2>Keeping the lights on</h2>
		<div class="feature-grid">
			<div class="feature-card">
				<div class="feature-icon">
					<svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
				</div>
				<h3>Issue Triage</h3>
				<p>Labels, deduplicates, and chases missing info — every 15 minutes, rain or shine.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="feature-card">
				<div class="feature-icon">
					<svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="7" r="4"/><polyline points="17 11 19 13 23 9"/></svg>
				</div>
				<h3>PR Review</h3>
				<p>Reads the diff, leaves honest feedback. Critical issues first, nits last. No feelings spared.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="feature-card">
				<div class="feature-icon">
					<svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"/></svg>
				</div>
				<h3>Health Reports</h3>
				<p>Monday morning summary of what's piling up, what's gone stale, and what needs you.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="feature-card">
				<div class="feature-icon">
					<svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M19.4 15a1.65 1.65 0 00.33 1.82l.06.06a2 2 0 010 2.83 2 2 0 01-2.83 0l-.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 00-1.82-.33 1.65 1.65 0 00-1 1.51V21a2 2 0 01-4 0v-.09A1.65 1.65 0 009 19.4a1.65 1.65 0 00-1.82.33l-.06.06a2 2 0 01-2.83 0 2 2 0 010-2.83l.06-.06A1.65 1.65 0 004.68 15a1.65 1.65 0 00-1.51-1H3a2 2 0 010-4h.09A1.65 1.65 0 004.6 9a1.65 1.65 0 00-.33-1.82l-.06-.06a2 2 0 012.83-2.83l.06.06a1.65 1.65 0 001.82.33H9a1.65 1.65 0 001-1.51V3a2 2 0 114 0v.09a1.65 1.65 0 001 1.51 1.65 1.65 0 001.82-.33l.06-.06a2 2 0 012.83 2.83l-.06.06A1.65 1.65 0 0019.4 9a1.65 1.65 0 001.51 1H21a2 2 0 010 4h-.09a1.65 1.65 0 00-1.51 1z"/></svg>
				</div>
				<h3>Runs Itself</h3>
				<p>Cron jobs run triage, reviews, and reports on autopilot. Set it up once, then move on.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- How it works -->
	<section class="how-it-works">
		<h2>How it works</h2>
		<p class="section-desc">
			Built on <a href="https://hermes-agent.nousresearch.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hermes Agent</a>
			with a custom MCP server packing 28 GitHub tools.
			Authenticates as its own GitHub App — every action is clearly from the bot, not you.
		</p>
		<div class="architecture">
			<div class="arch-step">
				<span class="step-num">1</span>
				<div>
					<strong>Point it at your repos</strong>
					<p>List what you want watched in <code>.hermes.md</code></p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="arch-step">
				<span class="step-num">2</span>
				<div>
					<strong>You move on to other things</strong>
					<p>Cron jobs keep running — scanning for new issues, unreviewed PRs, stale items</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="arch-step">
				<span class="step-num">3</span>
				<div>
					<strong>Last Light gets to work</strong>
					<p>Labels, reviews, closes duplicates, writes reports</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="arch-step">
				<span class="step-num">4</span>
				<div>
					<strong>The repo stays healthy</strong>
					<p>Everything happens on GitHub — comments, labels, reviews. No extra dashboard to check</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Get started -->
	<section class="get-started" id="get-started">
		<h2>Light it up</h2>

		<div class="step-block">
			<h3><span class="step-label">Step 1</span> Install Hermes Agent</h3>
			<pre><code>curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/NousResearch/hermes-agent/main/scripts/install.sh | bash
source ~/.zshrc</code></pre>
		</div>

		<div class="step-block">
			<h3><span class="step-label">Step 2</span> Clone Last Light</h3>
			<pre><code>git clone https://github.com/cliftonc/lastlight.git
cd lastlight</code></pre>
		</div>

		<div class="step-block">
			<h3><span class="step-label">Step 3</span> Create a GitHub App</h3>
			<p>
				Head to <a href="https://github.com/settings/apps/new" target="_blank" rel="noopener">github.com/settings/apps/new</a> and create an app with these permissions:
			</p>
			<ul class="permissions-list">
				<li><strong>Issues</strong> — Read & Write</li>
				<li><strong>Pull Requests</strong> — Read & Write</li>
				<li><strong>Contents</strong> — Read & Write</li>
				<li><strong>Metadata</strong> — Read</li>
			</ul>
			<p>Generate a private key, download the <code>.pem</code> file, and install the app on your repos.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="step-block">
			<h3><span class="step-label">Step 4</span> Configure</h3>
			<pre><code>cp .env.example .env</code></pre>
			<p>Fill in your GitHub App credentials:</p>
			<pre><code>GITHUB_APP_ID=123456
GITHUB_APP_PRIVATE_KEY_PATH=./your-app.private-key.pem
GITHUB_APP_INSTALLATION_ID=789012</code></pre>
			<p>Then add your repos to <code>.hermes.md</code>:</p>
			<pre><code>## Managed Repositories
- yourname/your-repo
- yourname/another-repo</code></pre>
		</div>

		<div class="step-block">
			<h3><span class="step-label">Step 5</span> Pick a terminal backend</h3>
			<p>Last Light runs commands through Hermes Agent's terminal. By default it uses <code>local</code> — commands run directly on your machine. For isolation or remote execution, pick a different backend in <code>config.yaml</code>:</p>

			<div class="backends-grid">
				<div class="backend-card">
					<h4>Local</h4>
					<p>Commands run on your machine. No setup, no isolation. Good for getting started.</p>
					<pre><code>terminal:
  backend: local</code></pre>
				</div>
				<div class="backend-card">
					<h4>Docker</h4>
					<p>Sandboxed container with dropped capabilities, PID limits, and tmpfs. Needs Docker installed.</p>
					<pre><code>terminal:
  backend: docker</code></pre>
				</div>
				<div class="backend-card">
					<h4>Modal</h4>
					<p>Cloud VM sandbox. Ephemeral, scalable, great for evals. Needs a <a href="https://modal.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Modal</a> account.</p>
					<pre><code>terminal:
  backend: modal</code></pre>
					<p>Set <code>MODAL_TOKEN_ID</code> and <code>MODAL_TOKEN_SECRET</code> in <code>.env</code>.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="backend-card">
					<h4>SSH</h4>
					<p>Run on a remote server. Persistent shell with connection reuse. Good for beefy hardware.</p>
					<pre><code>terminal:
  backend: ssh</code></pre>
					<p>Set <code>TERMINAL_SSH_HOST</code> and <code>TERMINAL_SSH_USER</code> in <code>.env</code>.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="backend-card">
					<h4>Daytona</h4>
					<p>Managed cloud dev environment with stop/resume. Needs a <a href="https://daytona.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Daytona</a> API key.</p>
					<pre><code>terminal:
  backend: daytona</code></pre>
				</div>
				<div class="backend-card">
					<h4>Singularity</h4>
					<p>For HPC clusters and shared machines where Docker isn't available. Uses Apptainer/Singularity.</p>
					<pre><code>terminal:
  backend: singularity</code></pre>
				</div>
			</div>

			<p>All container backends support resource limits:</p>
			<pre><code>terminal:
  container_cpu: 1         # CPU cores
  container_memory: 5120   # Memory in MB
  container_disk: 51200    # Disk in MB
  container_persistent: true</code></pre>
		</div>

		<div class="step-block">
			<h3><span class="step-label">Step 6</span> Run it</h3>
			<pre><code>./lastlight</code></pre>
			<p>That's it. You can also run single commands:</p>
			<pre><code>./lastlight chat -q "Review the latest PR on yourname/your-repo"
./lastlight chat -q "Triage open issues on yourname/another-repo"</code></pre>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Built-in skills -->
	<section class="skills">
		<h2>Tricks up its sleeve</h2>
		<div class="skills-grid">
			<div class="skill">
				<code>/pr-review</code>
				<p>Review a PR with structured, severity-ranked feedback</p>
			</div>
			<div class="skill">
				<code>/issue-triage</code>
				<p>Label, deduplicate, and prioritize issues</p>
			</div>
			<div class="skill">
				<code>/repo-health</code>
				<p>Generate a health report with metrics and action items</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Schedule -->
	<section class="schedule">
		<h2>On autopilot</h2>
		<p class="section-desc">These run automatically, out of the box:</p>
		<div class="schedule-table">
			<div class="schedule-row header">
				<span>Job</span>
				<span>Frequency</span>
			</div>
			<div class="schedule-row">
				<span>Triage new issues</span>
				<span class="freq">Every 15 min</span>
			</div>
			<div class="schedule-row">
				<span>Check PRs awaiting review</span>
				<span class="freq">Every 30 min</span>
			</div>
			<div class="schedule-row">
				<span>Refresh GitHub token</span>
				<span class="freq">Every 50 min</span>
			</div>
			<div class="schedule-row">
				<span>Weekly health report</span>
				<span class="freq">Mondays 9am</span>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Footer -->
	<footer>
		<div class="footer-content">
			<img src="/logo.png" alt="Last Light" width="32" height="32" />
			<p>MIT License. Built with <a href="https://hermes-agent.nousresearch.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hermes Agent</a>. <a href="https://github.com/users/cliftonc/projects/4" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Roadmap</a>.</p>
		</div>
	</footer>

</body>
</html>

<style is:global>
	:root {
		--gold: #F0B429;
		--orange: #E8752A;
		--teal: #1A7A8A;
		--teal-dark: #135E6B;
		--navy: #1B2735;
		--bg: #0C1117;
		--bg-card: #141B24;
		--bg-card-hover: #1A2332;
		--border: #1E2A38;
		--text: #C9D1D9;
		--text-muted: #7D8694;
		--text-bright: #ECEFF4;
		--mono: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
		--sans: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
	}

	* {
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0;
		box-sizing: border-box;
	}

	html {
		scroll-behavior: smooth;
	}

	body {
		background: var(--bg);
		color: var(--text);
		font-family: var(--sans);
		line-height: 1.6;
		-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
	}

	a {
		color: var(--gold);
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: color 0.2s;
	}

	a:hover {
		color: var(--orange);
	}

	h1, h2, h3 {
		color: var(--text-bright);
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	code {
		font-family: var(--mono);
		font-size: 0.85em;
		background: var(--navy);
		padding: 0.15em 0.4em;
		border-radius: 4px;
		color: var(--gold);
	}

	pre {
		background: var(--navy);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: 8px;
		padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
		overflow-x: auto;
		margin: 0.75rem 0;
	}

	pre code {
		background: none;
		padding: 0;
		font-size: 0.82rem;
		color: var(--text);
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	/* Nav */
	nav {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: center;
		padding: 1.25rem 2rem;
		max-width: 1100px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.nav-logo {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.6rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--text-bright);
		font-size: 1rem;
	}

	.nav-logo:hover {
		color: var(--gold);
	}

	.gh-link {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		padding: 0.4rem;
		border-radius: 6px;
		transition: color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
	}

	.gh-link:hover {
		color: var(--text-bright);
		background: var(--bg-card);
	}

	/* Hero */
	.hero {
		min-height: 80vh;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
	}

	.hero-content {
		flex: 1;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		text-align: center;
		padding: 2rem;
		max-width: 700px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.hero-logo {
		width: 140px;
		height: auto;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		filter: drop-shadow(0 0 40px rgba(240, 180, 41, 0.15));
	}

	.hero-name {
		font-size: 1rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		letter-spacing: 0.15em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}

	h1 {
		font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem);
		line-height: 1.15;
		margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
	}

	.accent {
		color: var(--gold);
	}

	.subtitle {
		font-size: 1.15rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		max-width: 520px;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		line-height: 1.65;
	}

	.hero-actions {
		display: flex;
		gap: 0.75rem;
	}

	.btn {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		padding: 0.65rem 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		font-weight: 500;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		transition: all 0.2s;
		border: 1px solid transparent;
	}

	.btn-primary {
		background: var(--gold);
		color: var(--bg);
		border-color: var(--gold);
	}

	.btn-primary:hover {
		background: #D9A025;
		border-color: #D9A025;
		color: var(--bg);
	}

	.btn-ghost {
		border-color: var(--border);
		color: var(--text);
	}

	.btn-ghost:hover {
		border-color: var(--text-muted);
		color: var(--text-bright);
	}

	/* Sections */
	section {
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 3rem 2rem;
	}

	section h2 {
		font-size: 1.6rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		letter-spacing: -0.01em;
	}

	.section-desc {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		max-width: 600px;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		line-height: 1.65;
	}

	/* Features */
	.feature-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
		gap: 1rem;
		margin-top: 1.25rem;
	}

	.feature-card {
		background: var(--bg-card);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: 10px;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		transition: border-color 0.25s, background 0.25s;
	}

	.feature-card:hover {
		border-color: #2A3A4D;
		background: var(--bg-card-hover);
	}

	.feature-icon {
		color: var(--teal);
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}

	.feature-card h3 {
		font-size: 1rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
	}

	.feature-card p {
		font-size: 0.88rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		line-height: 1.55;
	}

	/* How it works */
	.architecture {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.75rem;
		margin-top: 1.25rem;
	}

	.arch-step {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1.25rem;
		align-items: flex-start;
		padding: 1.25rem;
		background: var(--bg-card);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: 10px;
		transition: border-color 0.25s;
	}

	.arch-step:hover {
		border-color: var(--teal-dark);
	}

	.step-num {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		min-width: 32px;
		height: 32px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: var(--teal-dark);
		color: var(--text-bright);
		font-weight: 600;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
	}

	.arch-step strong {
		display: block;
		color: var(--text-bright);
		margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
	}

	.arch-step p {
		font-size: 0.88rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
	}

	/* Get started */
	.get-started {
		border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
		padding-top: 3rem;
	}

	.step-block {
		margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
	}

	.step-block h3 {
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.6rem;
	}

	.step-label {
		font-family: var(--mono);
		font-size: 0.7rem;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.08em;
		color: var(--teal);
		background: rgba(26, 122, 138, 0.12);
		padding: 0.2em 0.6em;
		border-radius: 4px;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.step-block p {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		margin: 0.5rem 0;
	}

	.permissions-list {
		list-style: none;
		margin: 0.75rem 0;
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
		gap: 0.4rem;
	}

	.permissions-list li {
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		padding: 0.4rem 0.6rem;
		background: var(--bg-card);
		border-radius: 6px;
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
	}

	.permissions-list li strong {
		color: var(--text);
	}

	/* Backends */
	.backends-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
		gap: 0.75rem;
		margin: 1rem 0;
	}

	.backend-card {
		background: var(--bg-card);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: 8px;
		padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
	}

	.backend-card h4 {
		color: var(--text-bright);
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
	}

	.backend-card > p {
		font-size: 0.82rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		line-height: 1.5;
		margin: 0.3rem 0;
	}

	.backend-card pre {
		margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
		padding: 0.6rem 0.8rem;
		font-size: 0.78rem;
	}

	/* Skills */
	.skills-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 1rem;
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
	}

	.skill {
		background: var(--bg-card);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: 10px;
		padding: 1.25rem;
	}

